00:00:52.220 --> 00:00:55.030
We're going to open it up.

00:00:55.030 --> 00:00:58.142
Now in order to get this one to go in half,
we're going to take the bottom edge and we're

00:00:58.142 --> 00:01:04.300
going to take it up to the quarter line up
on the top.

00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:10.520
We're going open that one up, and then take
the bottom up to this line, this one-quarter

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:11.520
