00:01:18.929 --> 00:01:21.939
Make sure that when you do it on the other
side, that you're just going up to the fourth

00:01:21.939 --> 00:01:24.369
line and not that eighth line.

00:01:24.369 --> 00:01:30.149
Fold that one in half and then fold this one
up to the bottom like that.

00:01:30.149 --> 00:01:35.670
Open it up and then we're going to rotate
it to the side, and now we're going to divide

00:01:35.670 --> 00:01:37.409
this into fourths as well.

00:01:37.409 --> 00:01:44.509
So go ahead and take the bottom edge there,
fold that up to the middle, and then open

00:01:44.509 --> 00:01:46.700
it up.

00:01:46.700 --> 00:01:50.310
One more time there, that'll give you the
