00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:31.920
Now we're going to make a diagonal fold that's
three blocks in.

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:38.620
So take the bottom edge right here, fold it
up to the top of the this line right, so there's

00:02:38.620 --> 00:02:41.640
