00:03:09.370 --> 00:03:10.520
So I'll show you again from here.

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:15.030
We're going to use this line right here, this
line right here, and this line coming across.

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:17.420
We're going to take three units, we're going
